New roof, hvac, water heater, flooring throughout (lvp, tile, carpet), updated bathrooms, countertops, appliances, paint, roof, garage doors, fixtures & more! All setting on 2 acres right outside of Cabot. Close to Cabot High School & minutes form I-67 access!   Don't miss your chance to have a great home this large & updated for UNDER 500k! Contact us for your private showing today.  Agent see remarks
